section_title: Synthesis report on Kyoto Protocol Article 3.2 (demonstrable progress)
sentences: The Secretariat introduced the issue ( FCCC/SBI/2006/INF.2 and FCCC/SBI/2006/INF.7 ).
China, for the G-77/CHINA, expressed concern at rising Annex I greenhouse gas emissions and delays in reporting.
The PHILIPPINES urged full implementation of commitments under Protocol Articles 10 and 11 (existing commitments, financial mechanism).
The EU said it is implementing all its commitments under the Kyoto Protocol.
Henriette Bersee (Netherlands) and Arthur Rolle (Bahamas) will coordinate informal consultations.
